data.description: Welcome to Lake Anna! Wonderful rambler with split bedroom design. Updated kitchen with flooring, microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher. Spacious updated country front porch and back deck. Primary bedroom is private with large ensuite bath. 2 additional bedrooms share a hall bath on the other end of the home.  Front loading one car garage. Optional POA $300/yr for boat ramp and common area access.
